  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Kay waseqa Diosniypata, Señorniy kaypi kashan.
 Tükuy creej bautizakun, Evangelio willakun./
 
[C]
 /Aleluya, aleluya,
 Kusiywan Diosninchejman takisaj./
 
[V2]
 /Jamuy ari kunampacha Señorman qayllaykukuy.
 Jesús salvasusqanta tukuyman willaramuy./
 
</lyrics></song>